						               													<description>Sagacity is an abstract strategy game where players will compete to core the agreed upon amount of points by connecting a line of four of their own pieces. The twist comes from the game's four tiered board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each tier has a clear plastic 5x5 grid. A line of four pieces can connect on a single level or by using all four of levels of the board either vertically, horizontally or diagonally. Each line of four pieces will score a single point. If a player is able to complete two lines of four pieces in a single turn they will score 3 points, and if a player is able to complete three lines of four pieces is a single turn they will automatically win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Similar to Connect Four, players will take turns adding a single piece to any unoccupied space on any of the four tiers. When all pieces have been placed if neither player has won, the pieces are removed and play continues.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
